    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/b3747b36c7950498e90d8b70a0c580b9.poster.avif?t=1762864613\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/b3747b36c7950498e90d8b70a0c580b9.webm?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/b3747b36c7950498e90d8b70a0c580b9.mp4?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一颗落向遥远小岛的陨落流星将水手从白日梦中唤醒，他更改了自己的航向，去往调查。登陆小岛之后，水手遇到了一个狡猾的老萨满巫师——他偷走了水手的爱花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/bb778ad240f4216d5294740cb4e0dd6a.poster.avif?t=1762864613\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/bb778ad240f4216d5294740cb4e0dd6a.webm?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/bb778ad240f4216d5294740cb4e0dd6a.mp4?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水手只有用上自己的聪明和才能，帮助萨满完成神秘仪式，让小岛重归以往的荣光。只有那时，他才能得回自己的植物挚爱，重新开始自己的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/3f1c658971e4874dd31595129e201565.poster.avif?t=1762864613\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/3f1c658971e4874dd31595129e201565.webm?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/3f1c658971e4874dd31595129e201565.mp4?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实现预言</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个岛屿沙盒中走出自己的道路——你永远不知道下一个拐角会出现什么！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助萨满让小岛重归以往的荣光。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解有趣的谜题，获得所需的物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑得更快，跳得更高，摔得更轻——只要携带合适的物品，一切皆有可能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你捡到的每件东西都可能成为获得更大东西的关键所在。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/d09f9328194bca88de85effac4ecf90b.poster.avif?t=1762864613\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/d09f9328194bca88de85effac4ecf90b.webm?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755950/extras/d09f9328194bca88de85effac4ecf90b.mp4?t=1762864613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
